title: Do you think Kim Kardashian is beautiful? - Quora

response.answer_text: She's got a natural, almost exotic beauty. She looks like she's of mixed blood with features that can appeal to people of different races and ethnicities. She's Caucasian, but her skin is toned a bit to pass as a fair-skinned African-American. She's got full lips, a curvy body and straight black hair that is styled in a simple yet sexy way. She's no dummy either. When she speaks, her voice is soft and feminine and she doesn't come off as a phony (to me at least). There are some genuine qualities to her that make her appealing. To me, she must have been what Cleopatra of Egypt must have been like. Comfortable with herself and her sexuality. And we know she's sexual by the way she dresses as well as the sex tape she made and the sexualized photos she has posed for on occasion. Add it all up and you get one sexy woman.
